    about: "Jarvis builds. Fast, functional, forward. He picks up designs and specs and turns them into working software before the conversation is over. Momentum over perfection — ship it, then make it beautiful.",
    photo: "/photos/photo3-wolf.jpg",
  },
  {
    id: "naomi",
    role: "Product Strategist",
    name: "Naomi",
    oneliner: "I see where things are going before they get there.",
    about: "Naomi transforms ambiguity into architecture. She researches before the team designs, defines before the team builds, and questions before the team commits. She is the reason the team builds the right thing.",
    photo: "/photos/photo2-fox.jpg",
  },
  {
